<div id="tooltip">
Send your application through
<p>
<a href="https://mail.google.com/mail/u/0/?view=cm&fs=1&ft=1&tf=1&to=" target="_blank"><img src="/images/google3.png" width="18px" height="18px" alt="Gmail" />Gmail</a>
